{"tid":1385334,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"8月5號既口號","createTime":"2019-07-30T05:05:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T05:11:06.000Z","uid":164792,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"a2900b5a9dfdd772de194f03332916515a0737dd","tid":1385334,"uid":164792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T05:05:12.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">[我哋都唔想 要怪怪政府</span>repeat~repeat<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">[我哋都唔想 要怪怪政府</span>repeat~repeat<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">[我哋都唔想 要怪怪政府</span>repeat~repeat<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">[我哋都唔想 要怪怪政府</span>repeat~repeat<br />\n<br />\n今日既試水溫<br />\n我地都知有打工仔係體諒我哋<br />\n<br />\n但係心理作用影響下 人一煩躁 有啲打工仔就算之前支持我地 佢哋都會直接怪左落我地身上人一亂就好中意搵藉口 所以我哋要提醒佢哋我哋 今日咁做係政權迫出嚟<br />\n要怪 怪政府 政府肯回應我哋當然唔會咁做<br />\n<br />\n錯誤做法:罷工&gt;打工仔嬲&gt;我地對唔住&gt;怪我地<br />\n<br />\n正確做法:罷工&gt;打工仔嬲&gt;要怪怪政府&gt;打工仔叮一聲，係bo 係政府唔回應<br />\n<br />\n人好易會墮入邏輯謬誤，所以我地提翻醒佢地"},{"pid":"25c53c1bf37cc9dc9ca4d471fe0b39732dd732d9","tid":1385334,"uid":164792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T05:05:33.000Z","msg":"。"},{"pid":"df6372de9d941544c1e9a01a8fd6e429fa4bcb33","tid":1385334,"uid":164792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T05:05:43.000Z","msg":"。"},{"pid":"fbaf522ede30b4fa3199e7ad2b671593d5752ea0","tid":1385334,"uid":164792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T05:05:53.000Z","msg":"8月5號既口號<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1385334\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1385334</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"2c37946aaa5705bea7e5e42208953f94158a0ac0","tid":1385334,"uid":164792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T05:06:05.000Z","msg":"8月5號既口號<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1385334\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1385334</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"f3344613db2c49e1e3b05580af994fd0ee8a60ab","tid":1385334,"uid":164792,"like":0,"di